el-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-chon-man-hinh-hien-thi-chuyen-dung-inno-cho-giao-duc\/#khong_gian_hoc_tap_chu_dong_trong_lop_hoc\" >Kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-chon-man-hinh-hien-thi-chuyen-dung-inno-cho-giao-duc\/#khong_gian_nghien_cuu_trong_phong_thi_nghiem\" >Kh\u00f4ng gian nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u trong ph\u00f2ng th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-chon-man-hinh-hien-thi-chuyen-dung-inno-cho-giao-duc\/#khong_gian_phong_giao_vu\" >Kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1o v\u1ee5<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-chon-man-hinh-hien-thi-chuyen-dung-inno-cho-giao-duc\/#khan_phong_trong_lop_hoc_co_quy_mo_lon\" >Kh\u00e1n ph\u00f2ng trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-chon-man-hinh-hien-thi-chuyen-dung-inno-cho-giao-duc\/#khong_gian_hoc_nhom\" >Kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ecdc nh\u00f3m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/tai-sao-chon-man-hinh-hien-thi-chuyen-dung-inno-cho-giao-duc\/#nhung_khong_gian_khac\" >Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng Inno gi\u00fap giao ti\u1ebfp hai chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u00f4ng qua m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 cho ph\u00e9p t\u0103ng th\u00eam t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"text font-regular \">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean nh\u1edd M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng Inno. M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Inno c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, bao g\u1ed3m l\u1ed1i v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8706\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Ung-dung-cua-man-hinh-Inno-trong-lop-hoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"573\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong_gian_hoc_tap_chu_dong_trong_lop_hoc\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>H\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m b\u00e0i t\u1eadp trong l\u1edbp. Ngo\u00e0i ra m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f9y bi\u1ebfn cho m\u1ed7i h\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao. (Thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh, L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c theo nh\u00f3m nh\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean t\u1ef1 tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y)<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8708\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Khong-gian-lop-hoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"601\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong_gian_nghien_cuu_trong_phong_thi_nghiem\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u trong ph\u00f2ng th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>H\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung l\u00e0m th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i v\u00ec c\u00e1c em c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy tr\u00ecnh th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cao. C\u00e1c em c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8703\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/D04.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong_gian_phong_giao_vu\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1o v\u1ee5<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00e1c gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn c\u00e1c t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u d\u1ea1y h\u1ecdc, n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c nh\u1edd m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a cho h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8704\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/D05.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khan_phong_trong_lop_hoc_co_quy_mo_lon\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00e1n ph\u00f2ng trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p LG khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 tham gia trong c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Th\u00f4ng tin r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 nh\u00ecn tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh l\u1edbn, nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8705\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/D07.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"601\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong_gian_hoc_nhom\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u00f4ng gian h\u1ecdc nh\u00f3m<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>H\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00e1ch nh\u1edd thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean gi\u00e1 s\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 c\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u00f3m, th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn t\u01b0 duy nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8709\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Khong-gian-thu-vien.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"599\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung_khong_gian_khac\"><\/span><strong>Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1c<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc nh\u00f3m, c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, t\u1ef1 do, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i. M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p LG c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1eddng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ed5 \u00edch v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng Inno gi\u00fap giao ti\u1ebfp hai chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u00f4ng qua m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 cho ph\u00e9p t\u0103ng th\u00eam t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c thu h\u00fat h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh\/sinh vi\u00ean nh\u1edd M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng Inno. M\u00e0n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9092,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8701","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8701","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8701"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8701